[normal]commenced legal proceedings against the Ho
[normal]me Office to challenge the level of financial support paid to people seeking asylum. The essence of 
[normal]this judicial review
[normal] is that the amount paid to destitute individuals and families (including those with children) is unlawful because it is insufficient to
[normal] meet their essential living needs or to provide a dignified standard of living.
